We do understand what may be excellent or good condition to us may not be excellent or good to you, so please inquire if you have any doubts or concerns.  Buyer pays return shipping.

We strive to have you as a continual customer and we stand by our representation. We are more than willing to answer any questions and / or concerns you may have prior to purchasing any item from our collection.
